00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:41.520
Kwagiulth First Nation in Fort Rupert, BC. And I'm one of the leaders

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:48.740
at Culture Saves Lives here on the Downtown Eastside of Vancouver. Culture

00:00:48.740 --> 00:00:55.320
Saves Lives is a program that focuses on bringing culture into stigmatized

