areas. A lot of the indigenous people down here haven't had access to

00:00:59.200 --> 00:01:04.440
culture in their lifetime. And we do our absolute best to bring that

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:08.140
in any facet we can. And the biggest part about Culture Saves Lives

