00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:58.080
to run away or maybe they're running away from something at home that

00:01:58.300 --> 00:02:03.620
they're not ready to face. And we just do our best to bring

00:02:03.620 --> 00:02:07.660
culture to people that have been deprived of that their whole lives.

00:02:07.940 --> 00:02:12.420
And it's not always true, there are a lot of people down here

00:02:12.420 --> 00:02:17.020
